{
  "script_id": "pagerank",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "互联网上有亿万个网页，谷歌凭什么把最好的排在最前面？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "早期谷歌的秘密武器，就是一个叫 PageRank 的算法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "它的核心想法很朴素：被越多重要网页链接的页面，本身就越重要。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "surfer",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "surfer-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/surfer-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "设想一个随机浏览者，在网页间不停地点击链接漫游。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "surfer",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "surfer-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/surfer-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "他停留在某个网页的概率，就是这个网页的 PageRank 值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "surfer",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "surfer-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/surfer-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "链接多、来源好的网页，浏览者更容易反复经过。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "matrix",
      "line_id": "mat-1",
      "filename": "matrix-mat-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/matrix-mat-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "把每个网页把自己的权重平分给它指向的链接，就得到转移矩阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "matrix",
      "line_id": "mat-2",
      "filename": "matrix-mat-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/matrix-mat-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "但浏览者不会永远点下去，有时会厌倦，随机跳到任意网页。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "matrix",
      "line_id": "mat-3",
      "filename": "matrix-mat-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/matrix-mat-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "阻尼因子 d 就是继续点链接的概率，通常取零点八五。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "iter-1",
      "filename": "iterate-iter-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/iterate-iter-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "让转移矩阵一次次作用到 rank 向量上，这就是幂迭代。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "iter-2",
      "filename": "iterate-iter-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/iterate-iter-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "每迭代一步，权重就沿着链接重新分配一次。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "iter-3",
      "filename": "iterate-iter-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/iterate-iter-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "很快向量趋于稳定，收敛到转移矩阵的稳态分布。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "拖动迭代滑块，看每个节点如何从均匀出发逐渐分出高低。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "换一个阻尼因子，感受它如何改变最终的排名格局。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "PageRank 把重要性建模成随机浏览者的稳态停留概率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "带阻尼的转移矩阵反复幂迭代，就收敛出这个分布。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pagerank",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pagerank/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "一个简单的链接投票，撑起了整个搜索时代，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
